---item_22 Cant Miss---
Type :: Gun
Slot :: Gun
Gun Definition :: [[Cant Miss]]
Rarity :: Exotic

On target hit, refund bullet to magazine.
For every 5 bullets that hit the enemy gain a 5% damage buff for 10 seconds. Stacks 5 times (25% max). If you miss or take damage then you lose all your buffs.
Each shot slows you down for a short time.

They call me Deadeye Joe. Cause I never miss, not because my eye is dead.

---gundef_Cant Miss---
Fire Speed :: 0.5
